    <title>使用nginx解决前后端分离跨域</title>
    <url>/2019/02/01/nginx/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="nginx-使用为了解决跨域问题"><a href="#nginx-使用为了解决跨域问题" class="headerlink" title="nginx 使用为了解决跨域问题"></a>nginx 使用为了解决跨域问题</h2><p>windows开发环境可本地运行nginx服务监听对应svn路径下的html页面<br>即可将对应路径为 ‘/apis’ 的ajax请求转发到 nginx.config 里 proxy_pass 对应的域名端口<br>以此避免跨域</p>
<h3 id="nginx-for-windows"><a href="#nginx-for-windows" class="headerlink" title="nginx for windows"></a>nginx for windows</h3><h4 id="启动命令"><a href="#启动命令" class="headerlink" title="启动命令"></a>启动命令</h4><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">start nginx <span class="comment">// 启动nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">nginx -s quit <span class="comment">// 完整有序的停止nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">nginx -s stop <span class="comment">// 关闭nginx ：快速停止nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">nginx -s reload <span class="comment">// 修改配置后重新加载生效</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h4><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sendfile        off; <span class="comment">// 设置不缓存js</span></span><br><span class="line">server &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        listen       <span class="number">3000</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        server_name  localhost;</span><br><span class="line">        location / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            root   F:<span class="comment">//项目文件//SVN_//抽奖//gzwh_Lottery_Front//trunk//lottery-page;</span></span><br><span class="line">            index  index.html index.htm;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        location /apis &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			      rewrite  ^<span class="regexp">/apis/</span>(.*)$ /$<span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			      proxy_pass   http:<span class="comment">//localhost:8086;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="nginx-for-linux"><a href="#nginx-for-linux" class="headerlink" title="nginx for linux"></a>nginx for linux</h3><h4 id="安装及启动"><a href="#安装及启动" class="headerlink" title="安装及启动"></a>安装及启动</h4><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install nginx <span class="comment">// 安装nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">rpm -ql nginx <span class="comment">// 查看安装路径</span></span><br><span class="line">service nginx start <span class="comment">// 启动</span></span><br><span class="line">service nginx stop <span class="comment">// 停止</span></span><br><span class="line">service nginx restart <span class="comment">// 重启</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="项目相关记录"><a href="#项目相关记录" class="headerlink" title="项目相关记录"></a>项目相关记录</h4><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">workespace4 工作区</span><br><span class="line">centos nginx.config 目录 /etc/nginx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 使用svn</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install -y subversion</span><br><span class="line">svn checkout  http:<span class="comment">//svn.com/path</span></span><br><span class="line">svn update</span><br><span class="line">path: <span class="regexp">/root/</span>project/gzwh_Lottery_Front/trunk/lottery-page</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>配置<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">user root; <span class="comment">// 解决403问题</span></span><br><span class="line">sendfile off; <span class="comment">// 关闭js自动缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">server &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  listen <span class="number">3000</span> default_server;</span><br><span class="line">  server_name localhost;</span><br><span class="line">  location / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    root /root/project/gzwh_Lottery_Front/trunk/lottery-page;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  location /apis &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    rewrite ^<span class="regexp">/apis/</span>(.*)$ /$<span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    proxy_pass http:<span class="comment">//localhost:8086;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>参考地址<a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000007116797" target="_blank" rel="noopener">yum 和 源码包 安装的 区别</a></p>
]]></content>
